closeup-of-thank-you-flower-bouquet-2023-11-27-05-34-07-utc.jpg?v=1709195576" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/closeup-of-thank-you-flower-bouquet-2023-11-27-05-34-07-utc.jpg?v=1709195576 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/closeup-of-thank-you-flower-bouquet-2023-11-27-05-34-07-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1709195576 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/closeup-of-thank-you-flower-bouquet-2023-11-27-05-34-07-utc_500x.jpg?v=1709195576 320w" width="1000" height="637" alt="Empowering Moms: Lifelong Learning with The Mandatory Training Group - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Empowering Moms: Lifelong Learning with The Mandatory Training Group - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-545_"/><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-546_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Rawpixel via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-548_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Mother's Day transcends geographical and cultural boundaries, uniting us in a common celebration of love and gratitude. It's a day that encourages us to pause and reflect on the invaluable contributions of mothers to our families and societies. In doing so, we also bring attention to the diverse experiences of motherhood, fostering a spirit of inclusivity and support for all mothers, regardless of their circumstances.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-550_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-551_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-552_">Organisations championing motherhood</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/flat-lay-floral-tulip-blossom-colors-mother-d-2023-11-27-04-54-50-utc.jpg?v=1709195649" s